nodes.title: UI Main Prompt

properties.defaultValue: A fantastical image of an (anthropomorphic farmer cat:1.2) navigating interchangeable levers and handles through a breathtaking, tranquil mountain trail, their fur plastered with greenery and trails of vibrant flowers. The cat's eyes are focused on the sky, the wind whipping through the leaves and the breeze filtering through the dense fog. Soft, warm lighting illuminates the scene, casting a soft glow across the landscape and creating a sense of depth and movement. painting, style of Jean-Baptiste Monge and Maximilien Luce

nodes.title: UI Secondary Prompt

properties.defaultValue: A serene and imaginative image of an (anthropomorphic cat in farmer clothes:1.25) tending to a flourishing garden and planting flowers, with the gentle movement of their fur as a support. In the background, a variety of curious flora and fauna gather around a lone, large, teardrop-shaped wooden table, where a colorful, verdant garden of succulent plants free-falls in harmony with the farmer. The earth beneath the farmer's feet is covered in roots, vines, and leaves that are inviting shade for the curious creature. illustration, style of Beatrix Potter and Richard Scarry
